: 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然，不是公務，只是我個人好奇的事情。", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#3"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——斬斷雙角的薩卡茲，除了我，你們還見過別人？", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#3"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_102_2"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "腐敗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_102_2"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213_1#4"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  誰鋸斷你們的角？", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#4"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  誰把——薩卡茲——當做實驗的奴隸和劊子手？", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#4"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_102_2"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "腐敗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_102_2"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213_1#2"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好吧。被馴服得真徹底。", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#2"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213_1#3"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  跟我走嗎？", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#3"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_102_2"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......什麼？", "name": "腐敗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_102_2"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213_1#3"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們這麼大塊頭，能幹很多活吧？我們可是在荒地上紮營的，最缺的就是勞動力——", "name": "托蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213_1#3"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_102_2"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你——", "name": "腐敗騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_102_2"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"n